{"tid":2069017,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所計劃成立可持續及綠色交易所資訊平台","createTime":"2020-06-18T05:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T02:39:18.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39ae16ed6cf745da938494e83d616207ad30b578","tid":2069017,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"港交所計劃成立可持續及綠色交易所資訊平台<br />\n2020-06-18 HKT 13:13<br />\n<br />\n港交所宣布，計劃成立可持續及綠色交易所「STAGE」，是亞洲首個可持續金融資訊平台，為投資者可持續及綠色金融產品信息及資源。<br />\n<br />\n交易所指，在初始階段STAGE將首先建立一個債券及交易所買賣產品(ETP)資訊庫，涵蓋在交易所上市的可持續發展債券、綠色債券和社會責任債券及與入環境、社會與管治(ESG)相關的ETP，並在今年稍後推出。<br />\n<br />\n交易所指，將隨市場發展逐步開發STAGE資訊平台，並考慮擴大覆蓋範圍，以引入更多資產類別和產品類型。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，亞太地區綠色債券發行量去年創新高，達到188.9億美元。至去年底，在本地市場處理和發行的綠色債券累計金額達到260億美元。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532780-20200618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532780-20200618.htm&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHrhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=11de0608\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532780-20200618.htm&h=39f20828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532780-20200618.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">亞洲首個可持續金融資訊平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3b89d3c378c4ed69b873170f834d4c8dbace94a5","tid":2069017,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"388<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"dec6bd03a453c00e2a276bd3f68ea883558bfaf9","tid":2069017,"uid":302784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"做咩事今年無啦啦係咁講ESG?"}]}